          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1694441277539-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate your <strong>cheddar</strong> <strong>cheese</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>beef</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong> and <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> in 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[65ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[80ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>Henderson's stock</strong></p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>Henderson's stock </strong>to the pan and cook for a further 1-2 min or until the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>burger mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1694441280336-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
