            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1694441282944-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potato[es] is crispy, remove the tray from the oven and carefully slice a cross through the centre, taking care not to cut all the way through</p><p>Fill each potato with the <strong>burger mix </strong>and top with the <strong>cheese sauce</strong></p><p>Return the tray to oven for 3-4 min or until piping hot – this is your <strong>nacho cheeseburger jacket potato</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1694441285707-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1694441285707-x400.jpg",
